description: A new boy Dylan Knight just moved in next door, he had heard rumors about the pornstar Trenton Ducati living in his building but he never thought he would actually meet him. Dylan had came home from the gym to find that he had left his keys, and his cell phone was dead. Dylan goes next door to ask to use a phone so he could call a cab to go back to the gym to get his keys but to his surprise Trenton Ducati answers the door. Taken back he forgets what he had knocked on the door in the first place for then remembers and explains the situation. Trenton being the nice guy he is of course lets the young stud use his phone and invites him in and this is what happens..
title: OverKnight
